donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n姐係冇變過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e9190bb8d659a32eb78b9335f483d62e219bd50","tid":1148104,"uid":196625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T09:19:25.000Z","msg":"很遺憾好多可有可無0既位置<br />\n好多時候都鐘意請蠢人<br />\n或者請個假人<br />\n最緊要係你顯示出黎容易控制唔會作反<br />\n而容易被人請<br />\n<br />\n一間公司真係需要幾多個醒人<br />\n被個醒人咁容易爬你頭咩"},{"pid":"5a4dc5dbe12b9d6c3c8b5a6256f3816692d1d4b3","tid":1148104,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T09:24:15.000Z","msg":"樓主加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4d1d76e3f3652457303ecef2f6747b8788bb8ae","tid":1148104,"uid":11310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T09:59:06.000Z","msg":"依家d死毒撚咁得閒出廢文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c020188dd4515c36f1dc1879416c4427f36094f","tid":1148104,"uid":198503,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"962509028b07bb5cd77a8b90ffd0e45374f35c3b","tid":1148104,"uid":62837,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T09:18:12.000Z","msg":"360度轉變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n姐係冇變過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T10:00:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0874d3e264658f14d96c1ebcd03f56175409052","tid":1148104,"uid":41423,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T10:02:13.000Z","msg":"樓豬表逹能力真係好差<br />\n有咁長時間打文都咁辭不達意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且無做proof read,唔係一個細心既人<br />\n下一份工應該過唔到試用期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5779da675ef526cf7db60e70c9d87be563445c8e","tid":1148104,"uid":58094,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T10:02:24.000Z","msg":"搵過年半工表示部份認同，有啲時候吹少少真係需要，太誠實反而係你未放低到過去嘅證明，只要係你可接受範圍就得。"},{"pid":"50e9c0b29af205d615b0b3592309220751368eb8","tid":1148104,"uid":74361,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T10:04:37.000Z","msg":"同一位老朋友聚舊, 佢依家撈得好掂, <strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">月入2-3萬以上</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d1128158029d9f98344e6fe49c89bf82eff7b57","tid":1148104,"uid":29540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T10:12:30.000Z","msg":"即係幾錢人工？"},{"pid":"7e8dcc15bed47faa561d4f77ebbe0fbb4ffdc3a5","tid":1148104,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T14:47:45.000Z","msg":"巴打想問你係點樣變得口才好？<br />\n0<br />\n12"},{"pid":"d13257571b7bbe090d896b64b0be3eebbd19b69b","tid":1148104,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"50e9c0b29af205d615b0b3592309220751368eb8","tid":1148104,"uid":74361,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T10:04:37.000Z","msg":"同一位老朋友聚舊, 佢依家撈得好掂, <strong><span styl